data.description: AWESOME, CRAFTSMAN STYLE, FAMILY HOME, CUSTOM BUILT IN 2006. LOCATED ON 2.00 GORGEOUS ACRES IN PIKE CO., GA. GREET GUESTS AS THEY ARRIVE WHILE RELAXING ON THE ROCKING CHAIR FRONT PORCH. ENTER THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME THROUGH THE TWO STORY GRAND FOYER WITH BRAZILIAN CHERRY HARDWOOD FLOORS THAT EXTEND THROUGHOUT THE MAIN LEVEL. FORMAL DINING ROOM WITH JUDGES PANELING. LARGE FAMILY ROOM WITH VAULTED CEILING AND A COZY WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE WITH STONE FACE AND HEARTH & A CUSTOM MANTEL. GOURMET CHEF'S KITCHEN FEATURES CUSTOM CABINETRY, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, DOUBLE OVEN, CENTER PREP ISLAND, COOKTOP WITH DOWNDRAFT VENTING AND A TRAVERTINE BACKSPLASH. LARGE MASTER SUITE ON THE MAIN LEVEL INCLUDES TRAY CEILINGS, A SITTING AREA AND HIS & HER CLOSETS. LAVISH MASTER BATH WITH TILED FLOOR, SEPARATE VANITIES, A JAZUZZI TUB AND A SEPARATE MARBLE SHOWER. POTENTIAL GUEST BEDROOM/OFFICE, HALF BATH AND LAUNDRY ROOM COMPLETE THE MAIN LEVEL. UPPER LEVEL ALSO FEATURES BRAZILIAN CHERRY HARDWOODS IN ALL 3 BEDROOMS w/WALK IN CLOSETS. ONE OF THE BEDROOMS CAN ALSO SERVE AS A LARGE BONUS ROOM. WALK OUT ATTIC SPACE BEHIND THE BACK BEDROOM. THE FINISHED TERRACE LEVEL IS PERFECT FOR AN IN-LAW SUITE, A TEEN SUITE OR GUESTS AS IT FEATURES A LARGE REC ROOM/FAMILY ROOM, DINING AREA AND FULL KITCHEN. THEATER ROOM/EXCERCISE ROOM, BONUS ROOM AND FULL BATH. DON'T MISS THE STORM SHELTER/ADDITIONAL STORAGE UNDER THE FRONT PORCH.  EXTRA UNFINISHED AREA FOR A WORKSHOP, LAWNMOWERS AND YARD TOOLS. THE BACKYARD OASIS FEATURES A FREE FORM, IN GROUND, SALTWATER POOL WITH A SPACIOUS CONCRETE LOUNGING SPACE FOR ALL OF YOUR OUTDOOR FURNITURE, TABLES AND CHAIRS.  OVERLOOKING THE POOL AREA IS A VERY LARGE DECK AND A PORCH WITH A PATIO BELOW. POOL AREA IS PRIVACY FENCED. LARGE, WIRE FENCED AREA FOR LIVESTOCK OR DOGS BEYOND THE PRIVACY FENCED AREA. THIS TRACT BACKS UP TO A WOODED AREA FOR ADDED PRIVACY. LOTS OF EXTRA SPACE ON THIS TWO ACRE TRACT FOR A GARDEN, CHICKENS, LIVESTOCK AND OTHER OUTDOOR IMPROVEMENTS. BUY THIS HOME AND I'LL BUY YOURS! *conditions apply EVERYDAY OPEN HOUSE. CALL AGENT FOR TIMES.
